description: Demolition of the existing buildings and comprehensive mixed-use redevelopment comprising a supermarket (Class A1), non-food retail units (Class A1), flexible floorspace for Classes A1/A2/A3/D1, and 245residential units (Class C3); together with associated car and cycle parking, highway works, public realm, amenity space, landscaping, plant and servicing arrangements.
